text: Andriy Mykhailychenko (born 11 August 1981) is a Ukrainian gymnast. He competed in six events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Ukraine Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint Petersburg
